{
  "version": "0.9.15",
  "build": "2026.07.14",
  "release_date": "2026-07-14",
  "changelog": [
    "security+feat: v0.9.15 — a large security-hardening pass, full Cloud-layout feature parity, temperature monitoring, and scale/perf work since 0.9.14.1. SECURITY: a broad authorization + input-validation sweep — per-VM ACL enforcement on VM detail/action/firewall routes, tenant-isolation gates across VMware / PBS / cluster / DR-drill / history / alerts / migration reads (IDOR/BOLA), SSRF guards on OIDC jwks_uri + template image_url + the ACME chain, RCE-hardening of ISO/template and ESXi-VMDK paths before root SSH, CSRF / HTTP-response-splitting / CSP tightening, tainted-log sanitisation (CWE-117) + vnc-ticket redaction, session invalidation on admin password reset, SIEM secret masking, per-cluster TLS ssl_verify gating for VNC/console, rollback path-containment (CWE-22), and dependency CVE bumps (Flask 3.1.3, PyJWT 2.13, pyasn1, pytest 9). Adds an AGPL §7(b) attribution term. CLOUD: the Cloud (Preview) layout reaches full parity with Corporate — complete SDN CRUD, Plugins / Scripts / Schedules, Config Drift / SIEM / Alert Channels / Update Manager, real HA / Networks / Storage / Site-Recovery components, a Reports group (Insights / Costs / Power & Carbon / API Health), Automation (Snapshot Policies / Templates), Topology + Compliance, and the real pegasus logo. FEATURES: per-host temperature monitoring gains history + a temperature alert metric (#601 jostrasser); opt-in 'show VM IDs in the sidebar' via My Profile (all 7 languages). PERF/SCALE: sidebar filter debounce + native windowing for 1000+ VM trees, TTL-cached VM-ACL + topology lookups, capped syslog TCP handlers. QUALITY: a full-stack integration test harness + 166 blueprint tests + security-invariant unit tests + a route-authz contract test, now run on every PR. Includes community PR #617 — snapshot-name validation (thanks @MatrixNeoKozak). SPONSORS: welcome TechniData AG Limited as a Silver sponsor. 💚"
  ],
